dsDescriptionValue.value:
For all wholesale trade establishments with payroll the data include number of businesses, sales, percent change in sales, annual payroll, percent change in payroll, number of paid employees, operating expenses, inventories, etc.

Geographic areas include the United States, States, SMSA, Standard Consolidated Statistical Areas (SCSA), area outside SMSA's, counties (or county equivalents), places, and balance of counties
